{"record_id":"pref-auto-push-remote","scope":"preference","title":"默认自动推送远端","content":"在本仓完成验证并准备发布后，默认按内容分批 commit，并使用 `cmd` 自动 `git push` 到远端。","source_type":"user_confirmation","source_ref":"user_confirmation:2026-03-27:auto_push_remote","last_verified_at":"2026-03-27T00:00:00Z","owner":"codex","expiry_or_revalidate_rule":"until_user_overrides"}
{"record_id":"pref-self-review-high","scope":"preference","title":"默认高强度自检","content":"默认采用高强度自检：正式改动后必须先完成自 review、必要时再经过独立 Reviewer subagent 审计、再跑定向测试和回归门；未通过 `review_passed + verify_passed` 前不报可交付、不自动推远端。","source_type":"user_confirmation","source_ref":"user_confirmation:2026-03-27:self_review_high;user_confirmation:2026-03-28:closed_loop_self_review;user_confirmation:2026-03-28:independent_reviewer_subagent","last_verified_at":"2026-03-28T00:00:00Z","owner":"codex","expiry_or_revalidate_rule":"until_user_overrides"}
{"record_id":"pref-workflow-layered","scope":"preference","title":"默认分层混合开发流","content":"默认开发流使用分层混合模式：L1/L2 走 `Spec Lite + Build/Verify/Observe`，L3/高风险/双仓升级到完整 Spec 和独立验收；同时对正式改动默认强制 `Spec -> Author -> Self-Reviewer -> Independent Reviewer -> Verifier -> Publisher` 闭环。","source_type":"user_confirmation","source_ref":"user_confirmation:2026-03-27:layered_mixed_workflow;user_confirmation:2026-03-28:closed_loop_self_review;user_confirmation:2026-03-28:independent_reviewer_subagent","last_verified_at":"2026-03-28T00:00:00Z","owner":"codex","expiry_or_revalidate_rule":"until_user_overrides"}
{"record_id":"pref-session-discipline","scope":"preference","title":"保留任务边界新开会话纪律","content":"即使引入结构化持久化记忆与 session capsule，任务边界仍默认新开会话；session capsule 只用于同一任务内减少重开。","source_type":"user_confirmation","source_ref":"user_confirmation:2026-03-27:task_boundary_new_session","last_verified_at":"2026-03-27T00:00:00Z","owner":"codex","expiry_or_revalidate_rule":"until_user_overrides"}
{"record_id":"pref-report-four-blocks","scope":"preference","title":"默认四段交付格式","content":"正式交付默认包含四段：改了什么、我自 review 发现并修了什么、我实际跑了什么验证、还没证明什么。","source_type":"user_confirmation","source_ref":"user_confirmation:2026-03-28:closed_loop_self_review","last_verified_at":"2026-03-28T00:00:00Z","owner":"codex","expiry_or_revalidate_rule":"until_user_overrides"}
{"record_id":"pref-proactive-gain-check","scope":"preference","title":"默认主动增益检查","content":"完成当前主问题后，默认做一次主动增益检查：若存在直接服务真实目标、验证成本低、失败代价小、可回退的优化点，补充 1-3 条；否则明确写“本轮无必要额外建议”。","source_type":"user_confirmation","source_ref":"user_confirmation:2026-03-28:proactive_gain_check","last_verified_at":"2026-03-28T00:00:00Z","owner":"codex","expiry_or_revalidate_rule":"until_user_overrides"}
